{
  "start": {
    "text": "Greetings, traveler. You've found me, a miner from the days when Tarnowskie Góry's veins ran rich with silver and lead. Do you seek tales from beneath the earth?",
    "options": [
      {
        "text": "Yes, tell me about your work.",
        "next": "work"
      },
      {
        "text": "What was life like in your time?",
        "next": "life"
      },
      {
        "text": "How did mining shape this town?",
        "next": "town"
      }
    ],
    "uuid": "42a3efd5-16f4-42b8-af35-30230e5695c0",
    "audio_file": "start_42a3efd5-16f4-42b8-af35-30230e5695c0.mp3"
  },
  "work": {
    "text": "Our days were long and the depths unforgiving. We extracted galena, the ore of lead and silver. The shafts were damp, and water was our constant adversary. In 1788, a steam engine from England arrived and helped drain the water.",
    "options": [
      {
        "text": "Tell me more about the steam engine.",
        "next": "steam_engine"
      },
      {
        "text": "What dangers did you face?",
        "next": "dangers"
      },
      {
        "text": "How did this affect the town?",
        "next": "town"
      }
    ],
    "uuid": "e1e25d41-4261-4695-8200-61d11b7024b4",
    "audio_file": "work_e1e25d41-4261-4695-8200-61d11b7024b4.mp3"
  },
  "life": {
    "text": "Life above ground was modest. Families were tightly connected to the rhythm of the mine. The Ordunek Górny granted miners rights and attracted workers from across Europe.",
    "options": [
      {
        "text": "What was the Ordunek Górny?",
        "next": "ordunek"
      },
      {
        "text": "Did many come from afar?",
        "next": "immigrants"
      },
      {
        "text": "How did families cope?",
        "next": "families"
      }
    ],
    "uuid": "7630ad0a-956b-4ad6-9e5a-87fc0b4e4b92",
    "audio_file": "life_7630ad0a-956b-4ad6-9e5a-87fc0b4e4b92.mp3"
  },
  "town": {
    "text": "The mine was the heart of Tarnowskie Góry. Its wealth drew scholars, merchants, and nobles. The town prospered when the mines thrived.",
    "options": [
      {
        "text": "Who visited the town?",
        "next": "visitors"
      },
      {
        "text": "What innovations emerged?",
        "next": "innovations"
      },
      {
        "text": "Did the town face hardships?",
        "next": "hardships"
